Update from 1.3.2 to 1.3.3

1) backup your files :
var/config/dbprofils.ini.php
var/config/defaultconfig.ini.php
var/config/havefnu.search.ini.php

Files
2) remove everything of the previous installation
3) upload the content of the archive on your website
4) restore your backup of var/config
5) set your havefnubb/modules/hfnuinstall/install/sql dir writable (chmod 755 or 777)
6) access to the following URL regarding your url engine :
* basic             : http://youresite.com/install.php?action=default:update_to_1_3_3&step=update
* basic_significant : http://youresite.com/install.php?action=default:update_to_1_3_3&step=update
* significant       : http://youresite.com/install/update/1_3_3

this will update your database and your config files with the correct version number of HaveFnuBB
